RACE.RACE_TEXT: SANDY RIDGE AT THE RED MILE RACE 1 220 Y Dirt CR: 76. Claiming Purse 17000. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 126 lbs.; Older, 128 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
